name: Unmitigated Gull
description:
Submission for Speed Jam 2023! 

You are a awful seagull here to eat everyone's food. Race the clock as you avoid crashing and getting caught, and victory will be yours.

Developed in Godot by Jeremy Rutledge (CliffRaven) and Noah MacAulay (interstitial).

Controls: arrow keys to fly, 'R' to reset, 'Esc' to pause
